    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily transportation. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are sound and have been well-maintained, ensuring it starts and runs consistently. However, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining from regular use. While it isn't a showpiece, it is a solid, functional car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
