      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and still has so much life left in it! It\u2019s been well-loved and kept in really nice shape, perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s ready to hit the road today. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
