    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) equipped with the S54B32 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six. This unit features a 6-speed Getrag 420G manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the dual-VANOS system has been completely overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The engine maintains a crisp throttle response thanks to its six individual throttle bodies and a recent precision valve adjustment. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road rash and the interior displays slight bolster wear consistent with use, the powertrain and drivetrain are mechanically sound and optimized for performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
