    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a beautiful shine, showing only the minor road-wear and light stone chips one would expect from a car that has been driven and enjoyed. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free environment with clean carpets and supple seating; while there is some light creasing on the driver-side leather, the interior remains remarkably preserved. Mechanically, this car is sound. It has been serviced regularly with full synthetic oil, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. All power features\u2014including the sunroof, heated seats, and premium audio system\u2014are fully operational. The air conditioning blows ice-cold, and the tires have plenty of miles left on them. We have kept up with all scheduled maintenance, ensuring this car is ready to hit the road immediately without needing any work. It\u2019s a solid, honest vehicle that balances performance with everyday practicality.",
